survey_response.review_text: Doctor clearly explained the condition and gave me options as to what I can do. Very refreshing to find a sincere Doctor at these times.
Doctor is more friendly and more patient in listening to patient's health issue. Happy to have found this doctor.
One of the Humblest, wise, dedicated, patient friendly doctor  I have ever come across... Fortunately we came to know while consulting for ortho.

An excellent, and friendly doctor.  She explained all aspects of the surgery and related procedures in detail.  We consulted her in her clinic (Prime Ortho and Shoulder Clinic) and in Apollo Cradle, but for getting better OT facility, she scheduled the surgery to be conducted at Apollo Hospital, Perungudi.  She coordinated with Apollo Hospital to book the OT and other required facilities and did the surgery at Apollo Hospital.  She has been of immense support to me , all along the treatment.  She was always available for discussions and to give us all guidance.  Because of the kind of care she provided, we felt like we were dealing with a family member.

There are no words to thank the doctor, for whatever care & support, that she has been giving to me all along the treatment. I would 100% recommend Dr. Bobby M.

review.practice_name: Prime Ortho and Shoulder Care Gynae and PCOD Care

survey_response.review_text: I visited Dr.Bobby for my 73 year old Mom's uterus related issue. Doctor was very patient in listening (and has got very good memory!) and after evaluating in detail, suggested to go for Hysterectomy. She also coordinated with Apollo Hospital and arranged for the surgery. During the entire time in the hospital, the doctor kept track of all issues and took personal interest. My mom is recovering and in good health now. I'm very happy to recommend Dr.Bobby and would be pleased to provide any reference.

Dr. Bobby is a very friendly person and carries an amazing personality. One feels so comfortable at the very first visit itself,that you open up your problems with much ease to her. She has been of immense support to me , all along the treatment. Her empathy is commendable and the positivity she emotes, have always made me develop a positive outlook. She was always available, in times of need. I am blessed to have the treatment under her. There are no words to thank the doctor, for whatever care & support, that she has been giving to me all along the treatment. I would 100% recommend Dr. Bobby for all the gyne problems. I wish 
Dr. Bobby all success.

Dr. Bobby is very friendly and makes you comfortable the very first time you meet her. She treated me for Scar Endometriosis and gave a clear picture of the further treatment and diagonasis. She really cares for you and always available through phone for any queries related to the treatment. I have never seen any doctor constantly staying in touch with the patient throughout the treatment.My surgery was planned in a short time but she organized and coordinated with the prerequisite tests, scans to be done etc. in few days and the surgery was done successfully without any chaos. I highly recommend Dr. Bobby for any Gynecological related issues as she is very much dedicated, well experienced, open for even simple questions and gives a clear picture of the treatment.
